metadata.name: Mother Plant #1591
metadata.description: The CannaThai420 Mother Plant NFT collection is the second collection in the CannaThai420 project, following from the Seed Plant collection. As the CannaThai420 broadly mirrors the growth process, cycle, and ecosystem of Bespoke’s legal cannabis cultivation in Thailand, the Mother Plant NFT collection portrays the important second stage. The Mother Plant NFT collection consists of 2,000 beautiful cannabis PFP NFTs where 1,995 pieces are generative NFTs each with a unique combination of 8 traits and 5 pieces are 1:1 art created by the talented CannaThai420 artists. The Mother Plant NFTs illustrate the vegetative stage of real-world cannabis growth. At this stage, the “cloning” process is used to allow growers to select the best and strongest cannabis plants and replicate them, allowing for rapid multiplication of the best plants in the crop.
